title: The Coven
description: I know now that I am not a regular teenager. I am a witch. A real blood witch. My parents are not my parents. My sister and I share no blood. Even in the coven I am too powerful now, too different to belong. I am alone except for Cal.Sixteen-year-old Morgan is not who she thought she was. But in that case, who is she?
author: Cate Tiernan
